cr_cultural_revolution_reflection|archive-date=2019-06-13|dead-url=no|author1=张炜}}</ref>。毛对中华人民共和国的建立作出了巨大的贡献<ref name=Britannica1980>[http://js.greengarden.org.cn/refbook/ShowDetail.aspx?Table=FERDOTHERINFO&ShowField=Content&TitleField=Title-ShowTitle&Field=OTHERID&Value=R20060622000A000081 毛泽东] {{Wayback|url=http://js.greengarden.org.cn/refbook/ShowDetail.aspx?Table=FERDOTHERINFO&ShowField=Content&TitleField=Title-ShowTitle&Field=OTHERID&Value=R20060622000A000081 |date=20130926095529 }}.不列颠百科全书(第15版)·第11卷. 1980.</ref>，但他发动或主导的[[大跃进|大跃进]]运动、[[文化大革命|文化大革命]]等各类政治运动也使人民和国家付出了巨大且惨痛的社会代价<ref name=Britannica>Stuart Reynolds Schram.[http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/363395/Mao-Zedong Mao Zedong] {{Wayback|url=http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/363395/Mao-Zedong |date=20140706163930 }},Encyclopedia Britannica Online.[2013-09-20]</ref>，据各方估计造成了数千万中国人的非正常死亡<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":2" /><ref name=":4" /><ref name=":6" /><ref name=":1">{{cite web|title=大跃进究竟饿死多少人？|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20131017/c17famine/|author=储百亮|date=2013-10-17|website=《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191022173715/https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20131017/c17famine/|archive-date=2019-10-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":7">{{cite web|title=《毛泽东的大饥荒》在香港发行|url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%AF%9B%E6%B3%BD%E4%B8%9C%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E9%A5%A5%E8%8D%92%E5%9C%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%91%E8%A1%8C/a-15426267-0|date=2011-09-29|website=[[德国之声|德国之声]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191117022646/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%AF%9B%E6%B3%BD%E4%B8%9C%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E9%A5%A5%E8%8D%92%E5%9C%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%91%E8%A1%8C/a-15426267-0|archive-date=2019-11-17|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{cite web|title=毛泽东逝世周年：崇毛为习近平带来难题|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-41209600|author=|date=2017-09-08|format=|publisher=[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]（BBC）|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180305033523/http://www.bbc.com/z