*1月，[[彭真|彭真]]等人为此事起草了《[[二月提纲|二月提纲]]》，将辩论局限在学术角度，不以政治角度批判<ref name=文革Ch2>{{cite web |url=http://v.book.ifeng.com/book/ts/32353/2474566.htm |title=试图控制局势的《二月提纲》,文革前夜的中国 |accessdate=2019-07-07 |archive-date=2014-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141015080022/http://v.book.ifeng.com/book/ts/32353/2474566.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。未经毛泽东同意，[[彭真|彭真]]将此提纲下发全党<ref name=翁衍慶>{{cite book |author=翁衍慶 |title=林彪的忠與逆 9/13事件重探 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=hyn6OmgWYDgC&pg=PA111 |date=2012-07-01 |publisher=新銳文創 |isbn=978-986-6094-93-4 |pages=110 |access-date=2019-07-07 |archive-date=2015-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150321162645/http://books.google.com/books?id=hyn6OmgWYDgC&pg=PA111 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
